window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Aden and team have won the day, but not without paying a price.</p> <p>Some traitors have been reveals and others defeated.</p> <p>He has gained the resources of an entire robotics company and with it gained a measure of independence, but for every solution there seems to be another question.</p> <p>Aden will do what he does best: survive and push on.</p> <p>The key difference between now and the rest of his life is that he doesn't have to do it alone.</p>"; 
